# 03-scoped-probes-mid.sh — mid-aggregation scoped-probe handlers for portable_doctor()
# Extracted from part-02-portable_doctor.sh per flywheel-08jug (Phase 6.8).
#
# Pattern: bash dynamic scoping (luzk7 + blmd8 precedent). Each handler reads
# caller's locals: $REPO_ABS, $JSON_OUT, $scope.
#
# Reuse note: this file depends on _scoped_probe_run + _scoped_probe_emit_missing_script_fail
# from 02-scoped-probes-pre.sh (sourced before this file by the entry preamble).
# Phase 6.8 added two more args to _scoped_probe_run (base_path + doctor_form)
# to cover the 2 mid-probes that use $HOME/.local/bin/<binary> instead of the
# default $REPO_ABS/.flywheel/scripts/<basename>. The other 4 mid-probes fit
# the original pattern and could call _scoped_probe_run directly; thin wrappers
# here exist for self-documentation and for symmetry with the 11 pre-probes.

